"The circle of life" continues to work as it should, young men being trained into Alpha's and young girl's stupidly giving into their lust till eventually it runs out and they realize "oops" they burned all their other bridges and now they have nothing. Honestly "Senpai"  lucked out, while the chick's going to go through what his childhood friend did when Coach was done with her, unlike her though she doesn't have a "convenient" male  childhood friend to hook up with and take advantage of afterwards LOL.

The funny part is, this can be similar to how it is IRL, once the girl turns "legal", she wants nothing to do with the "boys her age" and starts pursuing the "older mature men", till eventually she hits "the wall" (retirement in the terms of this story LOL) and the older mature men move on to the next "young thing" as she's left going for the "younger men" who got jilted, becoming theirs...until eventually they become the "Older mature men" and drop them like a bad habit for the "young girls".

(Reasoning is how his older Childhood friend swooped down on him the moment the THOT broke up with him because Coach didn't want his "bitches" being around other guys...till he was done with them like what happened to the childhood friend. It's funny how the childhood friend moved in on him the moment his "ex" became the coach's "new girl" like he was the best she was going to get, likely hoping by the time the THOT's turn with Coach was over, he would fall in love with her and stick with her)
